9. O-O
10. Be3{ This is the best option for White. The other colors reversed defenses against the Four Knights English Mainline fall short. }
10. Bd7{ We need to bolster the defense on  c6  to assure that our pawn structure remains intact. Our mainline in the English Symmetrical continues  here.  }
